Usage: report_path_groups [-help] [-name <group_name>] [-tcl_list]
                          [> <filename[.gz]>] [>> <filename[.gz]>]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-name <group_name>     # Specifies the name of the group which is to be
                       # reported. By default all groups are reported
                       # (string, optional)
-tcl_list              # Produces the report in Tcl list format instead of a
                       # tabular format (bool, optional)
> <filename[.gz]>      # Redirects output to specified file
                       # (redirect_operator, optional)
>> <filename[.gz]>     # Redirects output to specified file
                       # (redirect_operator, optional)